languages.text: "То есть вы хотите обобрать станцию, которой грозит голод, до нитки, а мне предлагаете присоединиться к пиру стервятников?"
"So you seek to rob the station blind — a station that is facing famine — and you're proposing that I join your little feast of vultures?"

languages.text: “也就是说，你们打算将这个正在面临饥荒的星站洗劫一空，还要我一起加入这场秃鹫的小小盛宴？”

languages.text: «¿Pretendes desvalijar una estación hambrienta y quieres que me una a tu pequeña bandada de buitres?».
languages.original_text: "So you seek to rob the station blind — a station that is facing famine — and you're proposing that I join your little feast of vultures?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Pretendes desvalijar una estación hambrienta y quieres que me una a tu pequeña bandada de buitres?».

languages.text: « Vous cherchez donc à drainer les dernières forces d'une station qui crie déjà famine, et vous me proposez de me joindre à votre nuée de vautours ? »
languages.original_text: "So you seek to rob the station blind — a station that is facing famine — and you're proposing that I join your little feast of vultures?"

traits.locale_text: « Vous cherchez donc à drainer les dernières forces d'une station qui crie déjà famine, et vous me proposez de me joindre à votre nuée de vautours ? »

languages.text: "Ihr wollt also die Station ausnehmen – eine Station, die vor einer Hungersnot steht – und schlagt vor, dass ich mich an Eurem kleinen Festmahl der Aasgeier beteilige?"

languages.text: "Kıtlığın eşiğindeki bir istasyonu soyup soğana çevirmek istiyor; yetmezmiş gibi bir de benden bu akbaba ziyafetine ortak olmamı mı bekliyorsunuz?"
languages.original_text: "So you seek to rob the station blind — a station that is facing famine — and you're proposing that I join your little feast of vultures?"

traits.locale_text: "Kıtlığın eşiğinde olan bir istasyonu… Kaşla göz arasında dolandırmayı mı planlıyorsunuz? Bu yetmezmiş gibi, bir de benden… Akbabaların ziyafetine ortak olmamı mı bekliyorsunuz?"
